{"tid":265989,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[人生交叉點] 公司全體員工使用盜版軟件","createTime":"2017-06-01T06:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T03:55:05.000Z","uid":22834,"like":684,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a6b2563478db40672b42342c36103cfde77da7","tid":265989,"uid":22834,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:14:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟係工程佬，啱啱喺間就快上市嘅中小企離職一個月。<br />\n<br />\n公司所有電腦set咗權限，唔允許任何員工自行安裝任何軟件，亦從來無裝過盜版軟件。<br />\n<br />\n但問題嚟喇。<br />\n<br />\n身為一個工程佬，每分每秒都用專業繪圖軟件係好合理。<br />\n<br />\n公司幾百人但只有不夠十個部電腦有繪圖軟件licenses，其他員工要正常工作只可以 <ins>自行從網上下載</ins> 或 <ins>自行從同事電腦複製</ins> 免安裝解破版專業繪圖軟件<ins>並於本機硬碟執行</ins>。<br />\n<br />\n公司一直唔買license，係知道員工唔想因為做唔到嘢而被上公指責而暗中使用盜版。咁樣，公司就可以慳咗一大筆軟件費，同時又可以免除法律責任，將矛頭直指向員工。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知向報海關舉報有無用，最後可能公司無事但舊同事遭殃。<br />\n<br />\n人生交叉點，求連登仔比個指示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 開名向海關舉報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 樓主收皮"},{"pid":"572eb325fa29e1f7c081a1bcfa7b2beb014a5703","tid":265989,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"你有冇證據呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做個好市民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a439fae1e24f66a3ae56ab07139503a55c7613","tid":265989,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:18:17.000Z","msg":"舉報等海關查"},{"pid":"0217025f72fb349131919e90dfe0b8094f5d8a9a","tid":265989,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:19:24.000Z","msg":"舉報啦"},{"pid":"9fc8d81b55d65134c2a5746f8d9815900fc433f2","tid":265989,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:23:34.000Z","msg":"你唔報益我<br />\n拎獎金"},{"pid":"5dedefb34430e5968c54d22e6bba3e0dddaaa634","tid":265989,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:24:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舉報等海關查</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e66e87d65f4361d25861657a06abe98b382aa0d","tid":265989,"uid":19542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:25:48.000Z","msg":"舉報完即走"},{"pid":"edcee3dec8f0603d06f46171d9a6bcb669dd7420","tid":265989,"uid":54733,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"員工自行下載軟件方便工作，或貪平購買盜版，老闆以往還可以隻眼開隻眼閉，但自從2008年版權（修訂）條例正式生效後，若僱員在貿易或業務過程中使用盜版軟件，管理層要負刑責，更不能以「唔知」為藉口卸責。最高刑罰是入獄4年及每件侵權物品罰款5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.hket.com/article/920537/免費軟件驗身%202年需求增4倍?category=m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F920537%2F%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E9%A9%97%E8%BA%AB%25202%E5%B9%B4%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E5%A2%9E4%E5%80%8D%3Fcategory%3Dm&d=hi8wbSk0%2F5PZXuKAsqUvlO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=7ba79500\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.hket.com/article/920537/免費軟件驗身%202年需求增4倍?category=m</a><br />\n<br />\n管理層扮唔知都冇用"},{"pid":"76773cfec4744e6b601ffb36973346471a14e5a9","tid":265989,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:26:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d940b568d9d019552661c28358a53ebba324331","tid":265989,"uid":15880,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"報啦<br />\n香港d 生番老闆最鐘意就慳錢<br />\n幫佢交番d 學費比海關啦"},{"pid":"3ba1542e3caa766af6678854990d999d92f7b351","tid":265989,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抵啦報啦"},{"pid":"ec9ed5c8fe55d5dc571352f7a76b56ff0bc65047","tid":265989,"uid":292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":